OURCE CONTROL MANAGEMENT (VERSION CONTROL)

git

distributed architechture 
every machine is a repo

git for windows

git init
run these commands to setup git user

git config --global user.name "yourname"
git config --global user.email youname@example.com

create files (touch command)
git status
git add .
git status
git commit -m "commit msg"
git reflog
initialise repo
git init

add files to staging area / index

git add filename

commit changes

git commit -m "message"

git status

git reflog




